            <li><a href="https://www.imo.org/en/OurWork/HumanElement/Pages/STCW-Convention.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IMO &mdash; STCW Convention (Standards of Training, Certification, and Watchkeeping)</a></li>
