            <li><a href="https://guide.freddiemac.com/app/guide/section/5303.4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Freddie Mac Single-Family Seller/Servicer Guide &mdash; Income Documentation</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.consumerfinance.gov/rules-policy/regulations/1026/43/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CFPB Regulation Z &mdash; Ability-to-Repay &amp; Qualified Mortgage Rule (Non-QM context)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.fhfa.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Federal Housing Finance Agency (FHFA) &mdash; GSE oversight</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="source-group">
          <h3 class="source-group-title">Surveyor accreditation</h3>
